## Bugs found & fixed during the build
- DP "free energy": nearest-node speed snapping made glides look lossless →
  fixed with semi-Lagrangian **interpolation** of the cost-to-go.
- P&G under-counting fuel: single-lap scoring wasn't periodic (banked KE) →
  fixed with **continuous multi-lap averaging** (`simulate_continuous`).
- DP chattering (87 micro-pulses): free restarts made constant-speed PWM optimal →
  added **engine on/off state + restart penalty**; DP now finds clean 4-pulse P&G.

## Possible next steps (not done)
- Plug in measured Cd, Crr, BSFC map for car-specific numbers.
- Add a measured engine BSFC lookup table (hook is in `vehicle.bsfc`).
- Per-corner strategy tuning if racing a tighter circuit where caps bind.
